message.body: Yes I did thanks for CCing me! She hasn't responded yet though right? I'm home on winter break right now though. I won't be back until mid-January. If Anne is available while I'm gone, definitely don't wait up for me!
Oh no, I'm definitely waiting bc it'll be nice to do it together. She responded and asked us for some of our available dates. I will offer some in late January?
Thanks Ingrid! Yes that's great. My first day back in Philly is January 12th. Any weekend day would be great, I can't wait
